SyntSpec.SSCarps

  • Uses of SSCarps in SyntSpec

    Subclasses of SSCarps in SyntSpec
    Modifier and Type
    Class
    Description
    class 
    ASCarps
    ASCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with an AS-specific genotype string and a new method for determining if a fish is "wild" or not
    class 
    FLCarps
    FLCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with the variable alleleCount, which is 0 by default.
    class 
    GDCarps
    GDCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with an GD-specific genotype string and a new method for determining if a fish is "wild" or not
    class 
    SSFLCarps
    SSFLCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with genotypes at 3 loci; a P, T, and L locus.
    class 
    SSGenomeCarps
    SSGenomeCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with its own set genome, where a wild genome is one with all lowercase letters
